After numerous reports that SK Khoza, who played Shaka in Mzansi Magic's popular soapie The Queen was leaving the show, he finally exited last night. His exit left the show's avid viewers divided, as some said they loved his relationship with Brutus. Twitter was not handling Shaka's exit well, as some said they would miss him. His co-star Dineo Langa, tweeted and wished him well.     